entry.value: INSERT INTO bestbuy.productsMonitor ( sku, name, modelNumber, manufacturer, regularPrice, salePrice, onlineAvailability, inStoreAvailability, customerReviewCount, customerReviewAverage, insertTimestamp ) VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?) ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE regularPrice = ${sql.args.5.value}, salePrice = ${sql.args.6.value}, onlineAvailability = '${sql.args.7.value}', inStoreAvailability = '${sql.args.8.value}', customerReviewCount = '${sql.args.9.value}', customerReviewAverage = '${sql.args.10.value}', insertTimestamp = CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
select distinct categoriesId, 1 as currentPage from bestbuy.bestbuyCategories bc where tracking = 1

select trim(sku) as sku, name, modelNumber, manufacturer, regularPrice, salePrice, onlineAvailability, inStoreAvailability, customerReviewCount, customerReviewAverage, ${now():toNumber()} as insertTimestamp from flowfile
